# Controlled CUPS — Sample Data

This file contains a subset of known, controlled CUPS used in the SIGEE-AGE project.

## Source

Converted from `data/seed/cups_controlados.csv`. All 23 entries are included.

## Schema

```json
{
  "<cups_key>": {
    "building_key": "<short uppercase code>",
    "building_name": "<display name>",
    "energy_type": "electricidad | gas_natural",
    "supplier": "<supplier full name>"
  }
}
```

## Usage

```js
// In index.html, load as a static JSON file:
const controlledCups = await fetch('./sample-data/controlled-cups.json').then(r => r.json());

// Lookup:
const info = controlledCups['ES0022000006212876CB'];
// → { building_key: 'VALLEHERMOSO', building_name: 'Vallehermoso', energy_type: 'electricidad', supplier: 'Iberdrola' }
```

